OL,3,CTeenage man murdered woman by driving
OL,4,Cinto her after taking nitrous oxide
OL,6,FA teenager has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurdering a woman by driving a car at
OL,8,Fher and others outside a club in
OL,9,FCardiff after taking nitrous oxide.
OL,11,F19-year-old Kian Bateman had been
OL,12,Fwatching from his car with the engine
OL,13,Frunning when Shelley Davies and her
OL,14,Fpartner David Bratcher had been
OL,15,Finvolved in "an altercation" with the
OL,16,Fdefendant's brother Kai.
