OL,3,CTeenage man murdered woman by driving
OL,4,Cinto her after taking nitrous oxide
OL,6,FIn the early hours of 27 September
OL,7,Flast year, a large group of people
OL,8,Fwere outside the Home Guard club in
OL,9,Fthe Ely area of the city following a
OL,10,Fgig. It was then that Kai Bateman
OL,11,Fthrew punches at 38-year-old Shelley
OL,12,FDavies, apparently in retaliation for
OL,13,Fher knocking a nitrous oxide balloon
OL,14,Fout of his mouth.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
