OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1777896668
OL,3,CTeenage man murdered woman by driving
OL,4,Cinto her after taking nitrous oxide
OL,6,FAfter a second punch to her head, Ms
OL,7,FDavies fell in the middle of the road.
OL,8,FSeconds later, Kian Bateman
OL,9,Faccelerated his Seat Ibiza car the
OL,10,Fshort distance towards Shelley on the
OL,11,Fground and Mr Bratcher stood in the
OL,12,Froad.
OL,14,FShelley Davies was taken to hospital
OL,15,Fwhere she later died of complications
OL,16,Ffrom her "terrible" injuries. Kian
OL,17,FBateman drove off without stopping,
OL,18,Fclaiming he had not realised he had
OL,19,Fhit anyone.
