OL,3,CTeenage man murdered woman by driving
OL,4,Cinto her after taking nitrous oxide
OL,6,FAt Cardiff Crown Court on Friday (1
OL,7,FMay), a jury of nine men and three
OL,8,Fwomen convicted Bateman of the murder
OL,9,Fof Shelley Davies. The Judge thanks
OL,10,Fthe jury and set a sentencing date of
OL,11,F3 July.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
